sky.f1.uk.title: F1 2025: The Story So Far
sky.f1.uk.description: Lando Norris bounces back to take pole alongside Charles Leclerc. Oscar Piastri and Lewis Hamilton share row two, while Max Verstappen starts down in P7 for Red Bull's home race. (29.06)

sky.f1.uk.title: F1 2025: The Story So Far
sky.f1.uk.description: It's lights out at Silverstone. Max Verstappen shares the front row with Oscar Piastri, while Brits Lando Norris, George Russell and Lewis Hamilton round out the top five. (06.07)

sky.f1.uk.title: F1 2025: The Story So Far
sky.f1.uk.description: It's lights out at Spa. With eyes on the weather, Lando Norris and Oscar Piastri lock out the front, while Charles Leclerc starts P3. Lewis Hamilton bids to fight through the field. (27.07)

sky.f1.uk.title: F1 2025: The Story So Far

sky.f1.uk.title: F1 2025: The Story So Far

sky.f1.uk.title: F1 2025: The Story So Far

sky.f1.uk.title: F1 2025: The Story So Far

UAndDavejavu.uk.title: James May's Things You Need To Know About Science
UAndDavejavu.uk.description: Speed: James explains all we need to know about speed - including how to dodge a hurricane - with a fast-moving mix of animation and motion graphics. S2 Ep4

UAndDavejavu.uk.title: Border Force America's Gatekeepers
UAndDavejavu.uk.description: A huge shipment of cocaine is found hidden in the floor of a truck, a young man tries to enter the US to enrol in school, and a woman is caught smuggling fentanyl pills. S4 Ep3

UAndDavejavu.uk.title: Border Force America's Gatekeepers
UAndDavejavu.uk.description: A woman is caught trying to enter the US with a baby that isn't hers, a man wanted for a serious crime is intercepted, and a driver has a heart attack while crossing a bridge. S4 Ep4

E4Plus1.uk.description: The Tangerine Factor: When Penny breaks up with her boyfriend, Leonard plucks up the courage to ask her out. And each of them turns to Sheldon for advice about their date. (S1 Ep17)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Bad Fish Paradigm: Penny opens up to a reluctant Sheldon after a less-than-stellar first date with Leonard, putting him in the awkward position of having to keep a secret. (S2 Ep1)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Codpiece Topology: Seeing Penny out on a date with another guy sends a distressed Leonard rushing back to Leslie Winkle, much to Sheldon's dismay. (S2 Ep2)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Young Sheldon
E4Plus1.uk.description: Poker, Faith, and Eggs: When Mary has to rush George Sr to the hospital, the kids' grandmother Meemaw comes over to babysit for his three anxious offspring. (S1 Ep3/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Young Sheldon
E4Plus1.uk.description: A Therapist, a Comic Book, and a Breakfast Sausage: After choking on a sausage, Sheldon wrestles with a fear of solid foods and discovers comic books. (S1 Ep4/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Dark Knight Court: When Bart's accused of playing a prank on the school marching band - a prank he says he didn't commit - Lisa must step in to defend her brother in court. (S24 Ep16/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Pulpit Friction: A trendy new reverend recruits Homer as a deacon. Dry cleaners accidentally swap Marge's wedding dress for one of Krusty's clown costumes. (S24 Ep18/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Dead Hooker Juxtaposition: Penny develops a rivalry with a sexy female neighbour who moves into the apartment building and threatens to become the 'new Penny'. (S2 Ep19)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Hofstadter Isotope: Leonard is devastated when Stuart from the comic book shop chats up Penny. Even worse, she doesn't mind. Sheldon tries to scupper the budding romance. (S2 Ep20)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Classified Materials Turbulence: Things look up for Leonard when Penny makes a surprising revelation on her second date with Stuart. Howard sees a flaw in his NASA project. (S2 Ep22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Big Bang Theory
E4Plus1.uk.description: The Monopolar Expedition: Leonard and Penny reconsider their feelings for each other, but then Leonard is offered the opportunity to spend the summer working at the North Pole. (S2 Ep23)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: Last Exit to Springfield: Homer takes on Mr Burns in a labour struggle that rapidly spirals out of control after Homer leads the workers on strike. (S4 Ep17/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: The Simpsons
E4Plus1.uk.description: So It Has Come to This: The Simpsons' Clip Show: Bart's special April Fools' Day prank seriously misfires when the whole house explodes. (S4 Ep18/22)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Hollyoaks
E4Plus1.uk.description: Diane's shocked by what she finds on her son's phone. Dodger confides in Donny. And a family is torn apart...

E4Plus1.uk.title: New: Animal Control
E4Plus1.uk.description: Brand new series - Cats and Monkeys: US sitcom. Shred's on the rebound. Emily leads the team in an animal adoption competition. Patel stumbles across an investment opportunity. (S2 Ep2/9)

E4Plus1.uk.title: America's Next Top Model
E4Plus1.uk.description: Roberto Cavalli: The final two contestants - and Series 14 winner Krista White - walk for legendary fashion designer Roberto Cavalli, before the judging panel crown a champion. (S15 Ep13)

E4Plus1.uk.title: Gogglebox
E4Plus1.uk.description: On the box this time: Hunted, Bake Off: The Professionals, Made in Chelsea, Love in the Jungle, Top of the Pops 1992, Dickinson's Real Deal, and BBC News (PM's party photos). (S19 Ep15)

E4Plus1.uk.title: First Dates
E4Plus1.uk.description: Two diners decide to serenade their dates. Greig is looking for a feisty man, but is John's brutal honesty a step too far? And Hebe, who's 20, is on her first ever date. (S8 Ep8)
